params.params_: Struct with the parameters to sned across bridges - includes token, amount, receiver, srcChain, dstChain
params.signatures_: Array of signatures from the governors (message hash signed by governors )

params.amount_: The amount of tokens to send.
params.isSingle_: Whether the token is to be batched with other tokens to save gas or not.

addDstToken(uint16,address,(uint8,bytes3.notice: Adds a token to the dstTokens mapping (verified with the signatures)

addWrappedToken(uint16,address,string,st.notice: Adds a wrapped token to the respective mapping so it can be used across chains

depositToAaveV3(address,uint256,(uint8,b.notice: Approves a given token so it can be handled in aave lending pool

swiftReceive((address,uint256,address,ui.notice: Receives a batch of tokens, mints the wrapped versions and verifies the signatures.

swiftSend(address,uint256,address,uint16.notice: Sends a token to another chain.

withdrawFromAaveV3(address,address,uint2.notice: Claims rewards from aave (that will then be distributed to the governors)
